[30;1m250 | [0m[35m        # we can avoid dealing with boundary conditions using the cubic[0m
[30;1m251 | [0m[35m        # spline as the Parzen window.  We do this by increasing the size[0m

[30;1m150 | [0m[35m    "in order" processing of pending transforms ensures that all pending transforms have been applie[0m
[30;1m151 | [0m[35m    tensor before a non-lazy transform (or lazy transform that is executing non-lazily) is carried o[0m

[30;1m153 | [0m[35m    pending_operations. Note that there is only one mechanism for executing lazy resampling at prese[0m
[30;1m154 | [0m[35m    is expected to change in future releases.[0m
[30;1m155 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m156 | [0m[35m    Evaluation of pending transforms is performed under the following circumstances:[0m

[30;1m43 | [0m[35m            - ``"macro"``: calculate metrics for each label, and find their unweighted mean.[0m
[30;1m44 | [0m[35m                This does not take label imbalance into account.[0m
[30;1m45 | [0m[35m            - ``"weighted"``: calculate metrics for each label, and find their average,[0m
[30;1m46 | [0m[35m                weighted by support (the number of true instances for each label).[0m

[30;1m66 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m67 | [0m[35mdef _dfs(node, paths):[0m
[30;1m68 | [0m[35m    """use depth first search to find all path activation combination"""[0m
[30;1m69 | [0m[35m    if node == paths:[0m
[30;1m70 | [0m[35m        return [[0], [1]][0m
[30;1m71 | [0m[35m    child = _dfs(node + 1, paths)[0m
[30;1m72 | [0m[35m    return [[0] + _ for _ in child] + [[1] + _ for _ in child][0m

[30;1m319 | [0m[35m    gt_boxes = gt_boxes[gt_ind][0m
[30;1m320 | [0m[35m    gt_ignore = gt_ignore[gt_ind][0m

[30;1m53 | [0m[35m        set_alpha_to_one: each diffusion step uses the value of alphas product at that step and at t[0m
[30;1m54 | [0m[35m            For the final step there is no previous alpha. When this option is `True` the previous a[0m
[30;1m55 | [0m[35m            fixed to `1`, otherwise it uses the value of alpha at step 0.[0m
